text: is a Japanese footballer who plays for Iwate Grulla Morioka. ==Career== Younger brother of Ryo, Tsuyoshi Miyaichi was signed by Shonan Bellmare in 2014. After almost two years squad, he was firstly loaned to Mito Hollyhock during 2015.
